targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(time,1s),
  linkid AS metric,
  value
FROM link_info
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(time,1s)

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  averagebytes
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  averagepkts
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  maxbytes
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  maxpkts
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  totalbytes
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  totalflownums
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  switchid AS metric,
  totalflowrate
FROM switch_info
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  linkid AS metric,
  flag
FROM highlight_link
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  mac AS metric,
  path,
  cost_time,
  safe_route
FROM highlight_route

SELECT
  switchid,
  averagebytes,
  averagepkts,
  maxbytes,
  maxpkts,
  totalbytes,
  totalflownums,
  totalflowrate
FROM switch_info

SELECT
  mac,
  ip,
  average_flow_rate,
  maxflow,
  protocol,
  dst_port,
  life,
  visit_cnt
FROM flow_info
WHERE
  flag = 0

SELECT
  ip,
  mac,
